{"tid":1330381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［姊妹爬山到我地啦］港女親善反修例行動","createTime":"2019-07-18T14:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T16:38:15.000Z","uid":265949,"like":8,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d6deb87312441c18a709592b1a87ae999f11d4f2","tid":1330381,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:12:09.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係一個港女CD-ROM，受到尋日銀髮一族嘅啟發，有一個Idea希望想同咁多位連登仔針針佢，所以借朋友ac 出post 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗有好多姊妹同我一樣，係過去個幾月的抗爭中，每次見到有義士上前，都會覺得好內疚，點解自己咁無力同細膽，唔可以企到最前同佢地並肩作戰，之前每次抗爭，就算只係幫手傳物資，現場氣氛都已經好緊張好工恐怖，我唔能夠想像企係最前線嘅手足心入面究竟會有幾驚⋯⋯真心覺得欠左義士們太多太多。除左係區選投票或者而家參與捐錢同遊行外，真係好希望自己可以做到啲野幫到前線手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日見到銀髮族上街，我真係好感動，亦令到我出現左以下呢個想法，會唔會係勇武文宣記者和理非銀髮同議員之外，我地仲可以有多一個position 叫「港女」？<br />\n<br />\n各位一直未搵到自己position嘅姊妹，我號召大家一齊出奇招，發揮我地溫柔嘅力量，係抗爭期間瘋狂稱讚、多謝、關心同微笑攻擊藍衫嘅前線警員，而唔再係指住佢地尼Diu黑警，實行「港女親善反修例行動」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道我咁樣提議應該10個巴絲打有11個都D9我on9, 但大家係D9完我同家母後，希望花少少時間睇下我點解咁提議：<br />\n<br />\n1. 我地叫得班藍衫做毅進仔，係因為我地個個都知佢地係情緒同感覺行先過個腦，所以我地如果再嘗試用邏輯、道理，甚至係鬥兇嘅方法同佢地溝通，只會Keep係而家呢個死位到，有必要改變下策略，用啲佢地會明嘅方法尼溝通：以柔制剛。我唔想如果每次當更都有一班靚女追住去關心藍衫，不停提醒返佢地其實大家都係香港人，佢哋仲會完住唔受影響。英雄，或者狗雄都難過美人關（有靚仔港男都可以參與去現場讚Madam)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 大家見藍絲打咁多次人都可以被保護放走，就係因為D警員覺得佢地係自己人，幫到佢地出氣，打9我地呢啲佢地眼中嘅暴徒，佢地每次遊行出尼on duty，我唔信佢地心底完全無恐懼，但係佢地愈驚，然後愈恨我地，想搵我地出氣嘅時候，如果我地個個都變左好似藍絲咁微笑溫柔對住佢地，我唔信佢地軍心會完全唔動搖<br />\n<br />\n3. 呢個同時係文宜嘅一大重點，係佢地打9我地嘅同時我地仲做到呢啲動作，只要多加宣傳，一定會有助吸納中立同淺藍人士，甚至係家有藍絲嘅兄弟姊妹都可以多左個方向尼說服家人，話佢地知：「睇下啲示威者幾好呀，對啲打佢地嘅人都咁好，你仲話佢暴徒你會唔會內疚？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 當然啦我唔係話要係有衝突當下去對警員好，無故打市民嘅都係狗，唔值得我地去拍佢地頭對佢對好，加上我地係火上心頭時都無可能做到啲咩溫柔嘅動作，勇武嘅義士係前線要做咩就繼續做，我地只會繼續支持！但並唔係示威每一刻都係咁緊張，同之前有人提出過和理非同勇武要輪番上陣一樣，我相信港女都可以加入，係中間發揮溫柔攻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 我唔熟警隊架構，但我都肯定警隊入面實有好多派別，打人個啲速狗、高層同埋平時負責守下前線嘅藍衫，心入面諗嘅都一定好唔同，打9我地啲人嘅一定要追究，但如果平時無做其他野，我地就瘋狂地對佢地好，慢慢就會分化左打人同唔打人個批，更理想嘅就會係分化埋前線同高層！係而家已經有唔少警察家屬開聲D9高層同林鄭的同時，無論係咪有人吹風向，我地都要好好利用時機，嘗試分化前線藍衫同政權<br />\n<br />\n6. 無錯我係講緊要將We Connect 的力量推廣到Connect埋前線警員，我要林鄭個政府孤立無援！要佢問責落台！要全面撤回惡法！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 我知有好多人都憎到班狗入骨，但係如果我地都願意為五大訴求付出咁多，甚至肯連命都唔要，唔通只係叫我地放低憎恨，由<br />\n班姊妹出動去打動第二敵人，一齊打低第一敵人我地會做唔到？如果林鄭要拉一派打一派，最好的反抗手法就係我地拉返轉頭，打9林鄭！<br />\n<br />\n8. 我咁樣講唔係要放棄追究之前警察濫權，亦都唔可以對唔住之前被打被拉被逼到自殺嘅義士，成立獨立調查會係一定要！我最終目標甚至係要說服埋前線警員去支持成立，重建佢地嘅尊嚴 （點說服佢地就睇姊妹嘅功力啦）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9. 我知道大家都覺得班狗無一個係無辜，但係當我消極都好，如果我地做完呢啲野，只係感動到一個警員，等佢打前線時細力少少、避開要害少少，我已經覺得值，反正我地啲之前咩都做唔到，試下新招奇招又有咩唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果各位兄弟姊妹睇完覺得條橋唔得就歡迎係下面講下有咩唔好，唔得唔好咪諗過下一條。但如果ok 可行，不如又提議下係實際操作可以點再做得好啲？我諗到嘅就一定要係人數夠多，除左港女外，銀髮、媽媽都可以一齊加入！做到聲勢浩大先會有用。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我想借個位多謝每一個係運動中出心出力嘅兄弟姊妹，能夠係呢個最壞嘅時代遇上最好嘅你地，用盡創意，遍地開花，拯救香港，係我最最最感動的事。做香港人嘅野，有今生無來世！多謝大家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hg4Fydb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhg4Fydb.png&h=54e8f634&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5addfc314e3ed0f15d7be169c7f91f8e6af64af1","tid":1330381,"uid":138744,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"傳翻物資好d"},{"pid":"3d4ddf967da1b497ed3c29a38cb096bea2b418aa","tid":1330381,"uid":228437,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:15:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TOO MUCH</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"23469676a5aced233a645d56a1de351420e089a0","tid":1330381,"uid":34293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"on9  男女平等"},{"pid":"120b51198bc35c29ee5ec48da648f2b4af4833ce","tid":1330381,"uid":35249,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"雖然我係女權撚<br />\n但想講 絲打你今次做多咗少少"},{"pid":"d013f96cc73c4b14514b50429edf153466fadf51","tid":1330381,"uid":180402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:19:36.000Z","msg":"個氣氛唔會容許你咁做<br />\n佢地應該會覺得你玩野跟住48個鐘"},{"pid":"194e767adfaed34716cd13659fad12a219084b4d","tid":1330381,"uid":261236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"麻麻地喎sis"},{"pid":"6930ac0dac7c2dda5ab399bce4563ec4d9b59b4b","tid":1330381,"uid":488,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"等陣比班狗同廢老 非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdd1673c6252de2302d360bf569e0690e8c683f","tid":1330381,"uid":211461,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:21:52.000Z","msg":"屌 瘋狂讚黑警 不如讚義士好過<br />\n義士拎性命前途為香港奮鬥<br />\n女士們係咪應該慰問安撫下佢地先<br />\n如果真係咁想奉獻的話"},{"pid":"e5ca948bcfb68b88281a07f502691efeff046205","tid":1330381,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:22:46.000Z","msg":"唔理你爭取咩先，你用暴力就一定錯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9e7987a890cd1833ad35a741e3072429c9e9a4f4","tid":1330381,"uid":226959,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"用下個腦先出post唔該 呢家唔係講玩 要玩番屋企慢慢玩"},{"pid":"6c1f1ffdd430b24bff005b06bbe549b7f2b10821","tid":1330381,"uid":121040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"don't <br />\n其實前後線一樣咁重要<br />\n好多謝你地係後線back up我地<br />\n同埋唔洗神化我地前線<br />\n我地都只係香港人罷了<br />\n<br />\n多謝<br />\n前線人員上"},{"pid":"76d3996b40498979ce698c7b13dd2516a233bf00","tid":1330381,"uid":214727,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:26:30.000Z","msg":"港女唔係最缺乏溫柔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做多左喇"},{"pid":"7971cf2c001040102062672083a78c9238f07d40","tid":1330381,"uid":31215,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"你呢招2014有人諗過<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2014/10/1410020236241528-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F10%2F1410020236241528-600x400.jpg&h=9e69f43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.epochtimes.com.tw/upload/images/2014/10/02/107371_medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.epochtimes.com.tw%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F2014%2F10%2F02%2F107371_medium.jpg&h=ac547e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20141027/large/fe504p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20141027%2Flarge%2Ffe504p.jpg&h=9415da8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.epochtimes.com/i6/1410020236111528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.epochtimes.com%2Fi6%2F1410020236111528.jpg&h=6408b311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.epochtimes.com/i6/1410020235371528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.epochtimes.com%2Fi6%2F1410020235371528.jpg&h=97088661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後一收order 扑到我地死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61df43369dd6784d7ec6941c69b526d2751838f4","tid":1330381,"uid":68598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"咩年代呀 人地就恨不得去打9香港人 <br />\n仲諗住愛與和平 <br />\n唔怪得移花接木都有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdab6a813588ec1dcef1d1530d06971b73fc26ce","tid":1330381,"uid":121040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7971cf2c001040102062672083a78c9238f07d40","tid":1330381,"uid":31215,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"你呢招2014有人諗過<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2014/10/1410020236241528-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F10%2F1410020236241528-600x400.jpg&h=9e69f43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.epochtimes.com.tw/upload/images/2014/10/02/107371_medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.epochtimes.com.tw%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F2014%2F10%2F02%2F107371_medium.jpg&h=ac547e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20141027/large/fe504p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20141027%2Flarge%2Ffe504p.jpg&h=9415da8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.epochtimes.com/i6/1410020236111528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.epochtimes.com%2Fi6%2F1410020236111528.jpg&h=6408b311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.epochtimes.com/i6/1410020235371528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.epochtimes.com%2Fi6%2F1410020235371528.jpg&h=97088661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後一收order 扑到我地死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"咪就係，根本感化係冇用<br />\n同埋成班女出去係送頭<br />\n重記唔記得有個女仔比差佬扯到bra都露埋"},{"pid":"4475a633f7c8f2b43fab1ce122f0dc352d6953ff","tid":1330381,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"2014做過<br />\n唔work"},{"pid":"a82634dd60b13d45f268bcc24b22fe5727742e45","tid":1330381,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"又黎用愛感化佢地？<br />\n<br />\n.....得罪講句算鳩數吧"},{"pid":"623dae4f8873e6688c5656a1d3ca49d5de9c698e","tid":1330381,"uid":128522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20110301/photo/0301-00405-001b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20110301%2Fphoto%2F0301-00405-001b4.jpg&h=b15b73e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"328e9192945b8b96e31629d69cd1f6a4bcae0635","tid":1330381,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"如果你唸住遊行果陣做都可以既, <br />\n你地一班拎住海報係遊行路線對住沿路差佬文宣係可以<br />\n<br />\n但係對持緊果陣,  你地會可能會受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢加暫時冇咩和平對持, 基本上一行得近就已經推進開片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34e70e5a919e25692aa5ce8b7abdb7f633accfa","tid":1330381,"uid":218,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"唔好影衰港女唔該<br />\n好多女都好勇武<br />\n你咁做係減緊我方士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50a8c3802f561e63e2f417a259f307851ff1744","tid":1330381,"uid":19817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b34e70e5a919e25692aa5ce8b7abdb7f633accfa","tid":1330381,"uid":218,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"唔好影衰港女唔該<br />\n好多女都好勇武<br />\n你咁做係減緊我方士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"對持果陣真係唔好,<br />\n<br />\n真係會隨時衝突<br />\n<br />\n同埋勇武都未必會受  心唸JM9"},{"pid":"3c877db6c6c94f83b6864166d3e881dc9115024b","tid":1330381,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"too long did&rsquo;t read<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf9cdd64e4efd528320568835f2978b7313ac37","tid":1330381,"uid":255222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"女權撚表示 反對性別定型 寧願去出錢買物資或者做gym 操